OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FA man who helped provide a gun used to
OL,7,Fkill a woman on a doorstep in south
OL,8,FWales has been found guilty of murder.
OL,10,FRenaldo Baptiste is the sixth
OL,11,Fdefendant to be convicted for the
OL,12,Fmurder of Joanne Penney, who died
OL,13,Fshortly after suffering the fatal
OL,14,Fgunshot in March last year.
OL,16,FThe court heard that Baptiste, 39, was
OL,17,Falready serving a life sentence for a
OL,18,Fseparate murder when he helped supply
OL,19,Fthe gun used in Ms Penny's murder.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
