PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FThe jury heard about messages he'd
OL,7,Fsent from a prison phone, including
OL,8,F"This is the Welsh ting", believed to
OL,9,Frelate to an image of a firearm.
OL,11,FIn other messages, Baptiste referred
OL,12,Fto "a 38 Smith Wesson 10 sweets" -
OL,13,Fthought to be shorthand for 10 bullets
OL,14,F- and responded to a message referring
OL,15,Fto "leg shots only" with a laughing
OL,16,Femoji.
OL,18,FBaptiste claimed the "leg shots"
OL,19,Fmessage was a reference to weights of
OL,20,Fcocaine, not violence.
