OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FHe denied helping supply the weapon
OL,7,Fused in Ms Penney's murder, but was
OL,8,Funanimously found guilty by a jury.
OL,10,FMolly Ruth Cooper, from
OL,11,FLeicestershire, was found guilty by
OL,12,Fmajority verdict of supplying,
OL,13,Fpossessing, purchasing or acquiring
OL,14,Fammunition without holding a firearm
OL,15,Fcertificate.
OL,17,FDonna James and Laura John were
OL,18,Fconvicted of assisting an offender.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
