PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FFive others are already awaiting
OL,7,Fsentence for murder over the incident,
OL,8,Fwhich took place in Talbot Green in
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,FMarcus Huntley admitted firing the
OL,12,Ffatal shot.
OL,14,FJoshua Gordon, Jordan Mills Smith,
OL,15,FMelissa Quailey-Dashper and Kristina
OL,16,FGinova were found guilty of murder
OL,17,Ffollowing a previous trial.
OL,19,FTony Porter was found guilty of
OL,20,Fparticipation in the activities of an
OL,21,Forganised crime group.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
