PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FTwo other men have also pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto that offence and are due to be
OL,8,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,10,FCardiff Crown Court was told that
OL,11,FJoanne Penney, who was 40, was shot
OL,12,Fwhen she answered the door at the
OL,13,Fproperty at 10, Llys Illtyd, on March
OL,14,F9th last year.
OL,16,FThe jury were told that there had been
OL,17,Fno specific plan to target Ms Penney,
OL,18,Fbut there had been an intent to "shoot
OL,19,Fsomeone" at the address from which a
OL,20,Fdrugs gang "were prevented from
OL,21,Fselling drugs."
OL,26,@zD@aOU{D@HO]|D@LOU}D@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
