PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FIn the weeks leading up to the
OL,7,Fshooting, the gang - known as the
OL,8,F"RICO" group - had suffered a series
OL,9,Fof "humiliations" at the hands of a
OL,10,Frival group.
OL,12,FIn one incident, a gang member had
OL,13,Fbeen chased out of the house in Talbot
OL,14,FGreen before having his getaway car
OL,15,Frammed.
OL,17,FOn another occasion, a man linked to
OL,18,Fthe group was violently assaulted.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@FO]qD@DOUqD@QO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
