OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FHaving decided on a "show of
OL,7,Fstrength", the jury was told how a
OL,8,Ffive person convoy set off for Talbot
OL,9,FGreen on March 9th.
OL,11,FThe court heard that Quailey-Dashper
OL,12,Fknocked on the door of the house,
OL,13,Fwhile Mills-Smith kept watch.
OL,15,FWhen Ms Penney opened the door,
OL,16,FHuntley fired a single shot from close
OL,17,Frange.
OL,19,FThe three then made their way back to
OL,20,Fa car where Gordon and Porter were
OL,21,Fwaiting.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
