OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Ginova was at another
OL,7,Flocation using Gordon's phone to send
OL,8,Fmessages in an apparent bid to help
OL,9,Fthe gang cover its tracks.
OL,11,FThanking the jury of 7 women and 5
OL,12,Fmen, Mr Justice Fordham adjourned the
OL,13,Fcase for sentencing.
OL,15,FBaptiste and Cooper were remanded in
OL,16,Fcustody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
