CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780311775
OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of murder of
OL,4,Cwoman shot dead on doorstep
OL,6,FThe judge said he was "satisfied" that
OL,7,FDonna James and Laura John would not
OL,8,Fhave to go into immediate custody as
OL,9,Flong as "appropriately stringent" bail
OL,10,Fconditions were set.
OL,12,FAll the defendants will be sentenced
OL,13,Fat a later date.
